OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAs the bells of St Peter's Basilica
OL,8,Ftoll solemnly across the Vatican,
OL,9,Fcenturies-old rituals spring quietly
OL,10,Finto motion within the heart of the
OL,11,FCatholic Church.
OL,13,FThe death of Pope Francis marks not
OL,14,Fonly the passing of a spiritual leader
OL,15,Fbut the beginning of a deeply symbolic
OL,16,Fprocess rooted in history, ceremony,
OL,17,Fand sacred tradition.
