OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FFrom the ancient confirmation of death
OL,8,Fto the sealing of the papal apartments
OL,9,Fand the gathering of cardinals in
OL,10,Fconclave, these time-honored rites
OL,11,Foffer a rare glimpse into a world
OL,12,Fwhere modernity pauses.
OL,14,FHere, ITV News explains what happens
OL,15,Fin the wake of the pontiffs death.
OL,17,FA silver hammer to the head
