OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAs the Church prepares for life
OL,8,Fwithout Pope Francis, the Vatican
OL,9,Fenters a period known as the sede
OL,10,Fvacante - the "vacant seat" - marking
OL,11,Fthe interregnum between pontificates.
OL,13,FAt the centre of this transition
OL,14,Fstands the camerlengo, currently
OL,15,FCardinal Kevin Farrell, the Irish-born
OL,16,FAmerican who heads the Vatican's
OL,17,FDicastery for the Laity.
