OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAs well as being responsible for the
OL,8,FChurch's administrative and financial
OL,9,Ffunctions in the interim period, it is
OL,10,Falso Farrell's responsibility to
OL,11,Fformally confirm the pope's death.
OL,13,FIt has become a matter of legend that
OL,14,Fthis tradition was done by the
OL,15,Fcamerlengo gently tapping the Pope's
OL,16,Fhead with a silver hammer and calling
OL,17,Fout his name three times.
OL,19,FBut this ritual is thought to have
OL,20,Flast been practiced in 1878 when Pius
OL,21,FIX died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
