OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe camerlengo will still
OL,8,Fceremoniously call out Pope Francis'
OL,9,Fbaptismal name - Jorge Mario Bergoglio
OL,10,F- three times.
OL,12,FApartment taped up and ring smashed
OL,14,FNow the Pope's death has been formally
OL,15,Fannounced, the camerlengo will seal
OL,16,Fthe papal apartments and papers with
OL,17,Fred ribbons.
