OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FUnlike his predecessors, Pope Francis'
OL,8,Fresidency was far more modest than the
OL,9,Ftraditional apartments of the
OL,10,FApostolic Palace. Instead, he chose to
OL,11,Flive in the two-room Domus Sanctae
OL,12,FMarthae guest house.
OL,14,FFarrell will also be responsible for
OL,15,Fensuring the Pope's Fisherman's Ring
OL,16,Fand the lead seal, which is used to
OL,17,Fauthenticate official documents, are
OL,18,Fdestroyed so they are unusable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
