OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe Fisherman's Ring, traditionally
OL,8,Fworn by the pope, is rich in symbolism
OL,9,Fand history. Its standard design
OL,10,Ffeatures an image of Saint Peter, with
OL,11,Fthe reigning pope's name inscribed
OL,12,Fabove.
OL,14,FWhen a new pope is inaugurated, the
OL,15,Fpresentation of the Fisherman's Ring
OL,16,Fmarks a powerful moment: a symbolic
OL,17,Fpassing of responsibility from Saint
OL,18,FPeter to his latest successor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
