OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FDestroying the emblem historically
OL,8,Finvolved smashing the ring with a
OL,9,Fspecial hammer.
OL,11,FHowever, when Pope Benedict XVI became
OL,12,Fthe first pontiff in nearly 600 years
OL,13,Fto resign in 2013, the custom was
OL,14,Fadapted and rather than being
OL,15,Fdestroyed, his ring was defaced with a
OL,16,Fdeep cross chiseled into its surface.
OL,18,FThree caskets
