OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FWhile popes were once laid on a
OL,8,Ftraditional raised catafalque in St
OL,9,FPeter's Basilica, Pope Francis
OL,10,Frequested a more modest presentation -
OL,11,Fwith the body no longer placed on an
OL,12,Felevated bier.
OL,14,FSealing of the coffin
OL,16,FThe night before the funeral, the
OL,17,Fcamerlengo presides over the closing
OL,18,Fand sealing of the coffin, in the
OL,19,Fpresence of other senior cardinals. A
OL,20,Fwhite cloth is placed over the pope's
OL,21,Fface.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
