OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA bag containing coins minted during
OL,8,Fhis papacy is placed in the coffin
OL,9,Falong with a one-page written account
OL,10,Fof his papacy - known in Italian as a
OL,11,F"rogito," a word indicating an
OL,12,Fofficial deed.
OL,14,FFuneral and burial
OL,16,FPope Francis' funeral will draw global
OL,17,Fattention, with dignitaries, world
OL,18,Fleaders, and thousands of mourners
OL,19,Fexpected to attend a Mass in St
OL,20,FPeter's Square before he is buried.
