OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FPrior to his death, Francis reformed
OL,8,Fthe long-standing tradition which sees
OL,9,Fpontiffs buried inside the Vatican.
OL,11,FInstead he requested to not be buried
OL,12,Fin St Peter's Basilica or its
OL,13,Fgrottoes, but in the St Mary Major
OL,14,FBasilica across town.
OL,16,FHis choice reflects his veneration of
OL,17,Fan icon of the Virgin Mary that is
OL,18,Flocated there, the Salus Populi Romani
OL,19,F(Salvation of the people of Rome).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
