OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAfter every foreign trip, Francis
OL,8,Fwould go to the basilica to pray
OL,9,Fbefore the Byzantine-style painting
OL,10,Fthat features an image of Mary, draped
OL,11,Fin a blue robe, holding the infant
OL,12,FJesus who in turn holds a golden book.
OL,14,F"It's my great devotion," Francis told
OL,15,FMexico's N+ in revealing his future
OL,16,Fburial plans. "The place is already
OL,17,Fprepared."
