OL,3,CThree caskets and a smashed ring: The
OL,4,Cancient traditions after the Pope's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAs mourning turns toward the future,
OL,8,Fthe centuries-old process of the papal
OL,9,Fconclave begins 15 to 20 days after
OL,10,FPope Francis' death.
OL,12,FOf the 252 cardinals in the College,
OL,13,F138 are under the age of 80 and
OL,14,Ftherefore eligible to vote. They will
OL,15,Fgather in the Sistine Chapel under
OL,16,Fconditions of strict secrecy to elect
OL,17,Fthe next Bishop of Rome.
OL,19,FIn a ritual steeped in history and
OL,20,Fsymbolism, the doors of the Sistine
OL,21,FChapel will be locked behind them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
